msgstr "Partnerschaft"

#. module: bike_leasing
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_leasing.catalogue
msgid ""
"Performance and design were the key words during the conception of this "
"super car. No compromises were made to keep the pleasure of driving despite "
"those constraints."
msgstr ""
"Leistung und Design waren die Schlüsselwörter beim Entwurf dieses "
"Superautos. Es wurden keine Kompromisse gemacht, um trotz dieser "
"Einschränkungen die Freude am Fahren zu erhalten."

